title: Very Irresistible By Givenchy For Women. Eau De Toilette Spray 2.5 Ounces
description: Introduced in 2003. Fragrance notes: peony and musk, a lovely, romantic flavor. Recommended use: evening.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: Covergirl Natureluxe Mousse Mascara, Very Black 500, 0.27-Ounce
description: Experience luxury touched by nature with the NatureLuxe Collection. The light-as-air Silk Foundation takes the heavy weight out of your polished finish. Our Mousse Mascara leaves your lashes looking light and lifted, with up to 2X more volume vs. bare lashes. Complete your simply gorgeous look with Gloss Balm’s touch of soft color and sheen.
